transcript:
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Haan ji sir, yeh Venkatesh Engineering se baat kar rahe hain?
Customer: Haan, boliye.
Executive: Mr. Manohar se baat kar rahe hain sir aap?
Customer: Nahi, Manohar nahi.
Executive: Madam thoda airport pe hoon, thoda baad mein call kijiye mere ko. Airport pe hoon.
Executive: Sir aapka ek number change karne ke liye request aaya tha na?
Customer: Haan, woh toh hai lekin main abhi thoda airport pe hoon, baad mein phone kijiye.
Executive: Theek hai.
